callback interface when getting image

方法摘要

          callback function after get image failed, run on ui thread

          callback function when get image but image not in cache, run on ui thread.

          callback function after get image successfully, run on ui thread

          callback function before get image, run on ui thread

onPreGet

void onPreGet(java.lang.String imageUrl,
              View view)
callback function before get image, run on ui thread

参数：
imageUrl - imageUrl
view - view need the image

onGetNotInCache

void onGetNotInCache(java.lang.String imageUrl,
                     View view)
callback function when get image but image not in cache, run on ui thread.
Will be called after onPreGet(String, View), before onGetSuccess(String, String, View, boolean) and onGetFailed(String, String, View, FailedReason)

参数：
imageUrl - imageUrl
view - view need the image

onGetSuccess

void onGetSuccess(java.lang.String imageUrl,
                  java.lang.String imagePath,
                  View view,
                  boolean isInCache)
callback function after get image successfully, run on ui thread

参数：
imageUrl - imageUrl
imagePath - image path
view - view need the image
isInCache - whether already in cache or got realtime
